{"tid":1469971,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇可能整「法治」既文宣","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T02:09:15.000Z","uid":292414,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"559c7d280ee937f1338ec83ea6823065ebca47b7","tid":1469971,"uid":292414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:45:37.000Z","msg":"法治既基礎係講緊<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">當權者應該守法</span></span></strong> 權力得以約束<br />\n當權無法濫權 公義先得到彰顯 呢個先叫法治<br />\n市民守法與否係唔會破壞法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n市民唔守法係叫違反法律break the law<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係break the rule of law<br />\n無論示威者幾暴力都好都只係唔守法<br />\n係唔會有損法治 畢竟宜家唔係冇拘捕過人<br />\n但777同d狗成日出黎屈示威者破壞法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">司法獨立 無罪推定 三權分立<br />\n監叫警會 ICAC 陪審團制度<br />\n法律面前人人平等 疑點利益歸於被告<br />\n呢d先係法治既核心價值<br />\n示威者何德何能去破壞呢d野</span></span></em></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">從來係法治既建設上 市民既角色只係觀察者<br />\n有必要比更多人知道法治既意思</span></span></strong><br />\n唔好比d小人亂咁用呢個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8d32147c369d0c306b7e0737b70a49f7051e0c","tid":1469971,"uid":292414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:46:34.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"603410963469596e6b9ba8a50fdd5d12bc66be8c","tid":1469971,"uid":292414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:46:45.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"46684381b71b7b8e15183764dd6a6305b765f18f","tid":1469971,"uid":162327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:48:00.000Z","msg":"呢樣宣傳都好重要 比啲開始猶豫唔知自己出嚟為咩嘅人認清楚我地嘅目的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫停回覆散水論 失敗論 分化論<br />\n<br />\n講太多會磨滅大家嘅鬥志<br />\n<br />\n諗下為撤回惡法而犧牲自己太古義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗下無衝擊而失去右眼嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗下係元朗被無故襲擊嘅市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗下幾百個被捕嘅學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗下呢幾個月以嚟黑警嘅所作所為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗返起政府對我地嘅態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n毋忘612 721 811<br />\n<br />\n818有冇下場都好<br />\n<br />\n香港人<br />\n維園見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a859b2fcbf95b48259c83700061642564dc9e2a6","tid":1469971,"uid":198800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:49:39.000Z","msg":"呢個先係重點<br />\n推"},{"pid":"e4ec8e0a216dcb497e57e4f54669a01bd1bac72b","tid":1469971,"uid":292414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:50:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推呀 破壞法治既係d濫權既死仆街</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0882e4c7028ff8681fe22d6d09a198e80ed3639e","tid":1469971,"uid":292414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:57:20.000Z","msg":"自推100次"},{"pid":"1027b9e95be82028d41dacba400316a5aac2e840","tid":1469971,"uid":198800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:01:52.000Z","msg":"啲人覺得示威者違法=警察就可以濫權 非法打壓<br />\n仲會覺得好合情合理<br />\n成套法律係一個社會定奪對錯嘅共識<br />\n如果執法者唔嚴格遵守法律<br />\n法津就無咗佢嘅權威<br />\n成套制度根本就無意思<br />\n<br />\n屌 但係班撐警柒頭皮肯定話我地講撚晒 <br />\n呢啲嘢最多俾自己人睇吓算"},{"pid":"2e5ed580252481